## Triage (verified 2026-05-17 against character sheets, `docs/party.md`, and `notes/session_prep/circle_of_thunder.md`)

- **Real issues, fix in `session-summary.md`:** 1, 2, 4, 5, 8, 9, 13, 16, 17, 18, 19, 20, 21, 22
- **Real issues, need DM/player decision:** 10, 14, 23
- **Intentional mysteries (note in recap as open, don't try to resolve):** 15 (eastern-clan boy is a deliberate seed for the "Chosen" arc)
