## ISSUE 3: Boots of Elvenkind — Wrong Quest Attribution **[RESOLVED — false alarm]**

**Status:** Falcon is the patron of the Woodland Manse quest and the boots of elvenkind are his offered reward (DM confirmation 2026-05-17). The recap is correct as written. The Falcon's Lodge quest is a separate quest from the same patron with a different reward (studio wood). No fix needed in the recap.

