## ISSUE 8: Prutha — Described with Contradictory Characterization

**Location:** NPCs (Prutha)

**Issue:** The NPCs section describes Prutha as "a ruthless warrior committed to the Order of the Gauntlet" in the opening line, then separately describes him as someone who "follows the party like a puppy" and is "fiercely loyal." The Order of the Gauntlet commitment is not established in the party document.

**Evidence:** The party document identifies Prutha as "first Lathander convert" and "new orc ally" under collective resources. He is described as having pledged "to the drow cleric" (Valphine) and is part of Valphine's congregation (Brin, Giles, Prutha). There is no mention of Prutha having any affiliation with the Order of the Gauntlet. His loyalty is to Valphine and Lathander, not to the Order.

**Suggested Fix:** Remove "committed to the Order of the Gauntlet" from Prutha's NPC description. He is a Lathander convert and orc ally of the party, not an Order of the Gauntlet member.

