## ISSUE 13: Grannoc — Referenced Without Identification **[RESOLVED via prep — needs recap addition]**

**Status:** Grannoc is identified in the prep as the **Talosian anchorite at the Woodland Manse** preparing the same ritual the party just interrupted. He is the natural next antagonist. Additionally, the cryptic note's wording in the recap ("your storm holds Grannoc") is the wrong sense — per prep (`notes/session_prep/circle_of_thunder.md:133`) the line is "Your storm holds. Grannoc's does not. He is reckless; he will summon before the Lodge is ready" — i.e. **Flenz's storm-ritual was succeeding, Grannoc's is not.** That's a major framing error, since the recap implies Grannoc is being restrained ("held") by the storm rather than being a rival anchorite under-performing.

**Suggested Fix:** Add Grannoc to the NPCs section as the Talosian anchorite at the Woodland Manse. Correct the cryptic note quote to match prep wording. Frame Grannoc as the next-scene antagonist, not as a captive or victim of the storm.

